1 Day Ago Following the confirmation of the situation on Tuesday, a top government source in the know told SaharaReporters that Kyari may be moved to Lagos any moment from now in an attempt to save his life. Lagos has one of the most functional infectious diseases treatment and isolation centres in the country. 



